data.message: Also, feel free to email her directly at MaryLinker@ymail.com (yes, it's a "y").

message:
Hi All! 

There is big need for PIANO TEACHERS in the Edina/Bloomington area through a company called MusicLink. You would need a car. Piano experience required, but no teaching experience required. I've taught there the past two years and the lady that runs it is really great to work with. She sets up all the lessons and collects payments so all you would have to do is show up. Respond or message me if you're interested. I'd be happy to answer any other questions you might have. Thanks!
